betterquesting:10.desc:8:
Locate a witch's hut, obtain the scroll within, and use it to access the Nether.

(Unlocks the Nether. Give access to redstone ore in the nether, and chester recipe).

Locate an ocean monument, obtain the scroll within, and use it to access Kathairis.

(Unlocks the Kaithairis. Gives access to heart canister recipes). 

(Hint: A portal of stone with a heart of gemstone).

Locate the Greek Temple and obtain the tools inside.

(Gives access to grappling hook recipes and enchantments).

Repair and use an Ancient Tablet to gain access to the End.

(Gives access to Waystones recipes).

Locate a Nether Fortress and defeat its inhabitants. 

(Enables natural regeneration, gives access to brewing).

Locate a jungle temple, obtain the scroll inside, and use it to access the rifts.

(Unlocks the midnight dimension).

Locate a Sky Temple and obtain the enchanted stone inside. 

(Gives access to enchanting tables and F3 coords).

Locate a desert temple, obtain the scroll within, and use it to access Icaria.

(Unlocks Icaria. Gives access to diamonds recipe & enables keep inventory). 

(Hint: A gateway ablaze with ancient fire. S = dolomite pillar. B = dolomite pillar head. C = dolomite slab).
